" Conceal                                                               {{{
"----------------------------------------------------------------------
" set this option string in .vimrc to determine which items to conceal
"
"   c citations
"   d definitions
"   e escaped characters
"   f footnotes
"   h headers (setext underscore style only)
"   H headers (atx hash & setext underscore style)
"   l links
"   q smart quotes & typography
"   r rules
